<docs>
   <doc for="IActionUnit">
 <summary>
    <para> Represents an atomic undoable action unit to be added
       to an <see cref='System.ComponentModel.Design.IUndoService'/> implementation.</para>
 </summary>
 <remarks>
 <para>Actions that implement this interface are compatible with the <see cref='System.ComponentModel.Design.IUndoService'/> which is designed to allow 
    programs to implement action undo and redo functionality.</para>
 </remarks>
 <seealso cref='System.ComponentModel.Design.IUndoService'/>
 <seealso cref='System.ComponentModel.Design.ICompoundActionUnit'/>
   </doc>
   <doc for="IActionUnit.Description">
 <summary>
    <para>Gets or sets a description for the action.</para>
 </summary>
 <value>
    <para>A description for the action.</para>
 </value>
   </doc>
   <doc for="IActionUnit.NextActionType">
 <summary>
    <para>Gets the next action type for the action unit.</para>
 </summary>
 <value>
 <para>The <see cref='System.ComponentModel.Design.ActionType'/> this action unit 
    would be performing on its next activation, either an <see cref='System.ComponentModel.Design.ActionType.Undo'/> or <see cref='System.ComponentModel.Design.ActionType.Redo'/> action type.</para>
 </value>
 <remarks>
    <para> The next action type is
       either <see cref='System.ComponentModel.Design.ActionType.Undo'/> or <see cref='System.ComponentModel.Design.ActionType.Redo'/>. The value of this field indicates the type of operation that will be performed
       on the next call to <see cref='System.ComponentModel.Design.IActionUnit.DoAction'/> and depends on whether
       the action was last performed or undone.</para>
 </remarks>
 <seealso cref='System.ComponentModel.Design.ActionType'/>
   </doc>
   <doc for="IActionUnit.DoAction">
 <summary>
 <para>Performs the action encapsulated in this <see cref='System.ComponentModel.Design.IActionUnit'/>.</para>
 </summary>
 <returns>
 <para><see langword='true'/> if the action was successfully 
    carried out; otherwise, <see langword='false'/>.</para>
 </returns>
 <seealso cref='System.ComponentModel.Design.ActionType'/>
   </doc>
</docs>

